node.text:
Empowered women, empower women 💯❤️ TAG your girl 🙋🏼‍♀️
-
-
Ladies this is for you! So many of you have been loving my business focused stories lately. Damn the future is really female 😍🙌🏼 - I have been considering a few ideas so us fellow boss babes can link together. An online course • business boss babe events • creating a forum • Let me know your thoughts below 💗💗

Lower body circuit work 🔥 TAG your honeys training in lockdown 🙋🏼‍♀️🙋🏼‍♀️ - Always staying hydrated and recovered with my @womensbest BCAAS 💚
-
-
Ladies I’m throwing it back a week! I finished my awesome gym lower body weight circuit with this awesome free weight finisher.. but hey! All my girls training from home this is so perfect for you too! Definitely stealing it for my hotel quarantine session today 🙃
-
40 reps of each exercise, (20 per leg for single sided exercises) x 3 rounds = 600 reps 🔥🙏🏼
-
-
& oooooh peep this gym fit 😝💚
